50/** \file

52
53#ifndef WRITER_H_
54#define WRITER_H_
55
56#include "types.h"
57#include "packet.h"
58#include "crypto.h"
59#include "errors.h"
60#include "keyring.h"
61
62/**
63 * \ingroup Writer
64 * the writer function prototype
65 */
66
67typedef struct pgp_writer_t pgp_writer_t;
68typedef unsigned pgp_writer_func_t(const uint8_t *,
69 unsigned,
70 pgp_error_t **,
71 pgp_writer_t *);
72typedef unsigned
73pgp_writer_finaliser_t(pgp_error_t **, pgp_writer_t *);
74typedef void pgp_writer_destroyer_t(pgp_writer_t *);
75
76/** Writer settings */
77struct pgp_writer_t {
78 pgp_writer_func_t *writer; /* the writer itself */
79 pgp_writer_finaliser_t *finaliser; /* the writer's finaliser */
80 pgp_writer_destroyer_t *destroyer; /* the writer's destroyer */
81 void *arg; /* writer-specific argument */
82 pgp_writer_t *next; /* next writer in the stack */
83 pgp_io_t *io; /* IO for errors and output */
84};
85
86
87void *pgp_writer_get_arg(pgp_writer_t *);
88
89void pgp_writer_set(pgp_output_t *,
90 pgp_writer_func_t *,
91 pgp_writer_finaliser_t *,
92 pgp_writer_destroyer_t *,
93 void *);
94void pgp_writer_push(pgp_output_t *,
95 pgp_writer_func_t *,
96 pgp_writer_finaliser_t *,
97 pgp_writer_destroyer_t *,
98 void *);
99void pgp_writer_pop(pgp_output_t *);
100unsigned pgp_writer_passthrough(const uint8_t *,
101 unsigned,
102 pgp_error_t **,
103 pgp_writer_t *);
104
105void pgp_writer_set_fd(pgp_output_t *, int);
106unsigned pgp_writer_close(pgp_output_t *);
107
108unsigned pgp_write(pgp_output_t *, const void *, unsigned);
109unsigned pgp_write_length(pgp_output_t *, unsigned);
110unsigned pgp_write_ptag(pgp_output_t *, pgp_content_enum);
111unsigned pgp_write_scalar(pgp_output_t *, unsigned, unsigned);
112unsigned pgp_write_mpi(pgp_output_t *, const BIGNUM *);
113
114void pgp_writer_info_delete(pgp_writer_t *);
115unsigned pgp_writer_info_finalise(pgp_error_t **, pgp_writer_t *);
116
117void pgp_push_stream_enc_se_ip(pgp_output_t *, const pgp_key_t *, const char *);
118
119#endif /* WRITER_H_ */
